3. Integration Tests (packages/extension/src/test/integration/):
- extension.test.ts - Test extension activation, commands
- webview.test.ts - Test webview creation, messaging
- settings.test.ts - Test settings UI, persistence

4. E2E Tests (packages/extension/src/test/e2e/):
- chat-flow.test.ts - Full chat flow (open, send, receive)
- workspace-context.test.ts - Add workspace context, verify prompt
- conversation-history.test.ts - Create/load/delete conversations

5. Test Utilities (packages/extension/src/test/utils/):
- Mock VS Code API
- Mock server responses
- Test fixtures (sample messages, contexts)
- Helper functions

6. CI Integration (.github/workflows/extension-ci.yml):
- Add test step before build
- Fail CI if tests fail
- Generate coverage report

Acceptance Criteria:
